{
  "name": "axon-ide",
  "displayName": "Axon",
  "description": "Axon AI 编程助手 —— 内置 Agent 内核，深度集成编辑器",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "private": true,
  "publisher": "ysj",
  "license": "MIT",
  "icon": "media/icon.png",
  "galleryBanner": {
    "color": "#1e1b4b",
    "theme": "dark"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/ysjemmm/Axon"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/ysjemmm/Axon#readme",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/ysjemmm/Axon/issues"
  },
  "type": "commonjs",
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.95.0"
  },
  "categories": ["AI", "Programming Languages", "Other"],
  "activationEvents": ["*"],
  "main": "./dist/extension.js",
  "contributes": {
    "configuration": {
      "title": "Axon",
      "properties": {
        "axon.trustedCommands": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "default": [],
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "命令信任白名单：Agent 执行 `execute_command` 时，命中这里的命令将免人工授权直接放行（灾难性命令如 `rm -rf` 始终被拦截，不受此影响）。\n\n约定：\n- 精确整条：如 `npm run build`（只信任这一条）\n- 前缀（以 ` *` 结尾）：如 `git status *`（信任 `git status` 开头的所有命令）\n- 全部：`*`（信任所有命令，强烈不推荐）\n\n在审批弹窗里选择「加入白名单」会自动写入此项。内置只读命令（`git status`、`pwd` 等）已默认信任，无需在此列出。"
        },
        "axon.proactiveAwareness.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "AI 主动感知总开关：开启后，终端报错和诊断变化（仅用户操作）会在侧栏显示 badge 通知。"
        },
        "axon.proactiveAwareness.terminalErrors": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "检测用户终端中命令执行失败（非零退出码），并在侧栏展示通知。AI 使用的终端不受影响。"
        },
        "axon.proactiveAwareness.diagnostics": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "检测诊断（errors/warnings）数量增加时，在侧栏展示通知。仅在问题数增多时触发。"
        },
        "axon.inlineCompletion.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "启用 AI 内联代码补全（替代 Copilot）。开启后，输入代码时 Axon 会自动建议补全。"
        },
        "axon.inlineCompletion.provider": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "内联补全使用的 LLM Provider。留空则自动探测第一个已配置的 provider。"
        },
        "axon.inlineCompletion.model": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "内联补全使用的模型。留空使用 gpt-4o-mini。可选更快/更便宜的模型（如 deepseek-chat、glm-4-flash 等）。"
        },
        "axon.inlineCompletion.maxPrefixLines": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 80,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "补全时发送给 LLM 的光标前最大行数。减小可降低延迟。"
        },
        "axon.inlineCompletion.maxSuffixLines": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 30,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "补全时发送给 LLM 的光标后最大行数。"
        },
        "axon.inlineCompletion.maxTokens": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 128,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "LLM 每次补全返回的最大 token 数。"
        },
        "axon.inlineCompletion.temperature": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 0.1,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "补全模型的采样温度（0-2）。越低结果越确定，越高结果越多样。"
        },
        "axon.compaction.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "**滚动压缩（推荐开启）**：长对话中自动把早期消息压缩为摘要，让 AI 始终拥有充足上下文窗口。\n\n**开启**：对话再多也不撞上下文上限，节省 Token 费用；代价是早期对话细节会被摘要替代（摘要会保留关键决策和已完成操作）。\n\n**关闭**：完整保留每一条原始消息，AI 能回忆更多早期细节；代价是长对话后期可能因上下文超限被迫手动压缩，费用更高。\n\n工具结果的自动裁剪不受此开关影响（由下方 `#axon.compaction.toolResultKeepTurns#` 独立控制）。"
        },
        "axon.compaction.triggerTokens": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 30000,
          "minimum": 5000,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "触发滚动压缩的 Token 累计阈值。自上次压缩后，新增 Token 超过此值即异步触发一次压缩。\n\n- **值越小**：压缩越频繁，上下文体积维持越低，但压缩次数多（每次压缩消耗一次额外 LLM 调用）\n- **值越大**：压缩越懒，省调用次数，但上下文体积在压缩间期涨得更高\n\n默认 30000（约 10 轮工具密集型对话后触发）。"
        },
        "axon.compaction.keepRecentMessages": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 8,
          "minimum": 2,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "压缩时保留最近多少条消息的原文不压缩。\n\n- **值越大**：AI 能看到更多近期原文上下文，理解更连贯；但上下文体积更大\n- **值越小**：压缩更激进，体积更小，但可能丢失近期上下文细节\n\n默认 8（约 3-4 轮完整对话）。"
        },
        "axon.compaction.toolResultPruneChars": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 800,
          "minimum": 50,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "旧工具结果裁剪后保留的字符数。超过 N 轮（见下方设置）的工具结果会被截断到这个长度，超出部分用标记替代。\n\n- **值越大**：旧工具输出保留越多细节（如完整搜索结果、完整命令输出）\n- **值越小**：上下文更精简，但旧工具输出可能丢失有用信息\n\n`read_file` / `list_dir` 保留开头，`execute_command` / `search` 保留末尾。"
        },
        "axon.compaction.toolResultKeepTurns": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 2,
          "minimum": 0,
          "scope": "resource",
          "markdownDescription": "保留最近几轮对话中的工具结果不被裁剪。设为 0 表示裁剪所有非当前轮的工具结果。\n\n- **值越大**：AI 能回看更多轮的完整工具输出（如之前读过的文件内容、跑过的命令结果）\n- **值越小**：上下文更精简\n\n注意：此裁剪独立于滚动压缩开关——即使关闭滚动压缩，旧工具结果仍会按此设置裁剪。"
        }
      }
    },
    "viewsContainers": {
      "activitybar": [
        {
          "id": "axon-manage",
          "title": "Axon",
          "icon": "media/axon.svg"
        },
        {
          "id": "axon-powers",
          "title": "Axon Powers",
          "icon": "media/powers.svg"
        }
      ],
      "secondarySidebar": [
        {
          "id": "axon-chat",
          "title": "Axon",
          "icon": "media/axon.svg"
        }
      ]
    },
    "views": {
      "axon-manage": [
        {
          "id": "axon.relay",
          "name": "Relay"
        },
        {
          "id": "axon.skills",
          "name": "Skills"
        },
        {
          "id": "axon.mcp",
          "name": "MCP"
        },
        {
          "id": "axon.provider",
          "name": "Provider"
        }
      ],
      "axon-powers": [
        {
          "id": "axon.powers",
          "name": "Powers"
        }
      ],
      "axon-chat": [
        {
          "id": "axon.chat",
          "name": "Axon",
          "type": "webview"
        }
      ],
      "explorer": [
        {
          "id": "axon.customSkills",
          "name": "Skills",
          "icon": "$(mortar-board)",
          "visibility": "collapsed"
        }
      ]
    },
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "axon.newSession",
        "title": "Axon: 新建对话"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.focusChat",
        "title": "Axon: 聚焦对话面板"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.openRelay",
        "title": "Axon: 打开 Relay"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.deleteRelay",
        "title": "删除"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.openSkill",
        "title": "Axon: 打开 Skill"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.skill.create",
        "title": "新建 Skill",
        "icon": "$(add)"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.skill.delete",
        "title": "删除 Skill"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.skill.rename",
        "title": "重命名"
      },
      {
        "command": "axon.skill.import",
